data.description: Located on a peaceful sprawling 4.29 acre property is this unique 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom Barndominium. The design features an open concept floor plan in a rustic, repurposed pole barn reminiscent of an airy loft living space within a rural setting. The double garage (with wall separating) has doors that reach 12' & 14' and provides plenty of room for equipment, a workshop, car lifts, or even for running a small business out of;  the possibilities are endless! Summer of 2023 added features include a whole home Leaf filtration system, dishwasher, garbage disposal, commercial grade faucet/sprayer, powered anode for water heater, nitrate IMF filter, reconverted breaker panels, Yale keyless entry smart door lock, closet rack, freshly painted floors. There is also a newly added 1000 gallon septic tank with a 1200 sq ft chamber system with leach field and perimeter drain, new well and well pump. The side yard has recently been graded for RV parking. There are many potential uses for the land. It would make a scenic, private location for another house to sit on, or would be a gorgeous setting for a small organic farm, greenhouse or garden. Or, leave it as is and enjoy the land! Centrally located between Greenfield and Shelbyville. Minutes to New Palestine, 30 minutes to Downtown Indy. This is truly a must see property!
